Nguyen, please note that I have expressed some of the same thoughts you have concerning the lack of thought of the Vietnamese people by some Americans.  Not all think like that, however.  Thank you for your perspective.<br><br>
Barbara, keep up the work of the Asian American Writers' Workshop. I've visited your web site, and find it impressive.  You might drop a line to The Noodles Club at Portland State University (http://www.cs.pdx.edu/~anle/) to see if they might have any contributions to make to your book.  <br><br>
Keep in touch.
